@translation labeled en project



@(2)Say to @lab{1}the generals, @lab{3}thus says the šabra:


@(4)The surface of the Euphrates @lab{5}has overﬂowed as far as Tumal @lab{6}and
the army is making a huge ﬂood control reservoir. @lab{7}(But) it has spread
all the way to the Gišgidulla ﬁeld. @lab{8}The ﬂood waters rose to 1 ½
cubits (0.75m). @lab{9}If the sun does not come out, @lab{10}not even 7200 troops
will stand against it. @lab{11}A huge amount64 of land has already been
carried away!


@(12)The labor(force) is insufﬁcient for me. I am unable to ﬁnish the task!

@(13)It is urgent!


