#lem: X; zipaŋ[breath]N; X; u; asag[a demon]N; zi[life]N; u

14.	mu-ŋu₁₀ mu-zu-ta im-da-an-pàd
#lem: mu[name]N; zu[to know, learn]V/t; pad[to find, discover]V/t

