@translation labeled en project

@(1)Say to Enlil-massu, @lab{2}thus says Inim-Inana:

@(3)Everything they told me made me very happy.^1^

@(4)May Lamma, Ud-tila, Akala, Lugal-šu, @lab{5}Na<bi>-Enlil and Enlilalsag, @lab{6}scholars who preceded you, @lab{7}Nin-imma, your goddess and

@(8)Nidaba, lady of broad wisdom, @lab{9}give you wisdom.

@(10)Regarding what was written on the tablet, @lab{11}did you not know it’s
the case that the city does not settle accounts?

@(12 - 13)Lu-gina is sending you 2 shekels of silver, 1 garment and 2 shawls.
Take them! @lab{14}(But) your mother should not take the remainder of the
inheritance. @lab{15}It is urgent!

^1^ Literally: They spoke every word to me and I have become very happy.


