#lem: Nibru[1]SN; Isin[1]SN; du[(to be) all]V/i; en[cvne]N; tar[to cut]V/t

19.	ka-inim-ma èn-du na-rú-a eme-ŋir₁₅ ka-tar
#lem: kaʾinimak[incantation formula]N; endu[a song]N; narua[stele]N; emegir[the Sumerian language]N; katar[praise]N

20.	[x (x)] zà nam-gala-šè ga-ne-eb-zu-zu
#lem: u; u; zag[side]N; namgala[the art of lamentation singing]N; zu[know]

