#lem: u; u; kugsig[gold]N; diš[one]NU; gun[a unit of weight, talent]N; kugbabbar[silver]N; ugu[skull, pate]N; ŋar[put]

23.	[...] da-ra nam-bí-šub-bé-en
#lem: u; da[line, edge, side]N; šub[to fall]V/i

